statements: SELECT * FROM Financial_Reports WHERE participant_id = 123;
SELECT report_date, compliance_status FROM Financial_Reports WHERE report_id = 5;
SELECT report_id, participant_id, report_date, compliance_status FROM Financial_Reports WHERE report_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Financial_Reports WHERE compliance_status = 'Pending' ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT participant_id, report_date FROM Financial_Reports WHERE report_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT report_id, participant_id, report_date, compliance_status FROM Financial_Reports WHERE report_date = '2021-10-01';
SELECT * FROM Financial_Reports WHERE compliance_status = 'Compliant' ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT participant_id, COUNT(report_id) AS number_of_reports FROM Financial_Reports GROUP BY participant_id HAVING COUNT(report_id) > 1;
SELECT report_id, compliance_status FROM Financial_Reports WHERE compliance_status LIKE '%Not%' ORDER BY report_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM Financial_Reports WHERE participant_id = 1001 AND compliance_status IN ('Compliant', 'Non-Compliant') ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM regulatory_reports;
SELECT report_id, participant_id, report_date FROM regulatory_reports WHERE compliance_status = true;
SELECT participant_id, participant_name, registration_date FROM participants;
SELECT participant_id, participant_type FROM participants WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM regulatory_reports INNER JOIN participants ON regulatory_reports.participant_id = participants.participant_id;
SELECT * FROM regulatory_reports WHERE compliance_status = TRUE;
SELECT participant_name, registration_date FROM participants ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_reports FROM regulatory_reports WHERE participant_id = 1001;
SELECT participant_type, COUNT(*) as total_participants FROM participants GROUP BY participant_type;
SELECT participant_name, report_date FROM regulatory_reports INNER JOIN participants ON regulatory_reports.participant_id = participants.participant_id;
SELECT * FROM financial_market_participants;
SELECT participant_id, participant_name, industry_sector FROM financial_market_participants ORDER BY registration_date DESC;
SELECT report_id, report_date, compliance_status FROM regulatory_compliance_reports WHERE compliance_status = 'Approved';
SELECT participant_id, compliance_rating FROM compliance_history WHERE compliance_rating = 'High' ORDER BY compliance_date ASC;
SELECT report_id, participant_id, compliance_date FROM compliance_history WHERE compliance_rating = 'Low' ORDER BY participant_id ASC, compliance_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM regulatory_compliance_reports ORDER BY compliance_status DESC, report_date ASC
SELECT participant_name, registration_date FROM financial_market_participants WHERE industry_sector = 'Banking'

SELECT rh.report_id, rh.compliance_date, ch.compliance_rating FROM regulatory_compliance_reports rh JOIN compliance_history ch ON rh.report_id = ch.report_id WHERE rh.compliance_status = 'Compliant' AND ch.compliance_rating = 'A'

SELECT rh.report_date, ch.compliance_date, rh.compliance_status FROM regulatory_compliance_reports rh JOIN compliance_history ch ON rh.report_id = ch.report_id WHERE rh.compliance_status = 'Non-Compliant' OR ch.compliance_rating = 'B'
SELECT participant_name, industry_sector FROM financial_market_participants WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30'
SELECT * FROM client_accounts;
SELECT client_name, account_balance FROM client_accounts WHERE account_balance > 1000;
SELECT account_id, client_name, account_balance FROM client_accounts ORDER BY client_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE transaction_type = 'credit' ORDER BY amount DESC;
SELECT account_id, COUNT(transaction_id) AS num_transactions FROM transactions GROUP BY account_id HAVING COUNT(transaction_id) > 5;
SELECT * FROM client_accounts ORDER BY account_balance DESC;
SELECT client_name, account_balance FROM client_accounts WHERE account_balance > 1000;
SELECT client_name, transaction_type, amount FROM client_accounts JOIN transactions ON client_accounts.account_id = transactions.account_id;
SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE transaction_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY amount DESC;
SELECT report_name, report_date FROM compliance_reports WHERE compliance_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM report_transactions;
SELECT id, transaction_date, amount FROM report_transactions WHERE amount > 1000;
SELECT name, location FROM participant WHERE id = 1;
SELECT name, jurisdiction FROM participant JOIN regulatory_agencies ON participant.id = regulatory_agencies.id;
SELECT * FROM compliance_reports WHERE compliance_status = TRUE ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM report_transactions WHERE amount > 1000 ORDER BY transaction_date DESC;
SELECT participant.name, regulatory_agencies.name AS agency_name FROM participant INNER JOIN regulatory_agencies ON participant.id = regulatory_agencies.id;
SELECT * FROM compliance_reports WHERE report_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' AND compliance_status = TRUE;

SELECT participant.name, compliance_reports.report_date FROM participant INNER JOIN compliance_reports ON participant.id = compliance_reports.participant_id WHERE compliance_reports.compliance_status = FALSE;

SELECT participant.name, COUNT(compliance_reports.id) AS total_reports FROM participant LEFT JOIN compliance_reports ON participant.id = compliance_reports.participant_id GROUP BY participant.name HAVING total_reports >= 3;
